steps.html_instructions: Head west on E Pearl St toward S Lamar St
At the traffic circle, take the 2nd exit onto University Blvd
Turn right to merge onto I-20 W toward Vicksburg

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-20 W, follow signs for Vicksburg
Passing through Louisiana
Entering Texas
Keep right at the fork to continue on TX-557 Spur W, follow signs for US-80 W/Dallas
Take exit 44A to merge onto I-35E N toward Denton
Keep left at the fork to continue on TX-183 W, follow signs for Texas 183/Texas 114/Irving/DFW Airport
Keep right at the fork to continue on Hwy 114 W/TX-114 W, follow signs for Grapevine/Airport North Entry
Keep right at the fork to continue on Hwy 114 W/Rte 114 W/State 114 W/State Rte 114 W/TX-114 W
Slight right onto Rte 114 W/State 114 W/State Rte 114 W/TX-114 W

Merge onto TX-114 W/U.S. 287 N/US-81 N via the ramp on the left to Decatur/Bridgeport
Continue to follow U.S. 287 N
Keep right at the fork to stay on U.S. 287 N
Take exit 3A on the left toward US-287 N/Vernon/Amarillo

Take the ramp on the left onto I-40 W/U.S. 287 N
Continue to follow I-40 W
Entering New Mexico
Turn left onto the I-25 S/US-285 S ramp to Santa Fe
Turn right onto NM-466 N/Old Pecos Trail (signs for Historic US 66)
